Pantron had been in the cr chamber for 12 hours. He had of course had to have his spark removed so his body could be repaired. So he was yet offline. Bobertron walked into the room. One last gift for my friend. He took the spark and re emerged it into pantron's body. I will see you again. Bobertron left as fast as he came. Pantron not realizing what had happened jumped and ran to the hatch of the ship. But bobertron was way gone. I hope you find what you are looking for. For i know you'll return in our or my darkest hour.
